import numpy as np

def submatrix_with_n_numbers(matrix):
    count = 0
    rows, cols = matrix.shape
    for i in range(rows-1):
        for j in range(cols-1):
            if (matrix[i, j] == 144 and matrix[i+1, j] == 144 
                and matrix[i, j+1] == 144 and matrix[i+1, j+1] == 144):
                count += 1
    return count
